OL,3,CWales suffer World Cup heartbreak as
OL,4,Cdreams dashed on penalties
OL,6,FWales' dreams of reaching this year's
OL,7,FWorld Cup in North America were
OL,8,Fshattered after they lost on penalties
OL,9,Fto Bosnia-Herzegovina at the Cardiff
OL,10,FCity Stadium.
OL,12,FBrennan Johnson and Neco Williams
OL,13,Fmissed the decisive penalties as Craig
OL,14,FBellamy's side lost 4-2 on penalties
OL,15,Fafter the game finished 1-1.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/18
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
