OL,3,CWales suffer World Cup heartbreak as
OL,4,Cdreams dashed on penalties
OL,6,FWales: Darlow; Williams, Lawlor,
OL,7,FRodon, Dasilva; Ampadu (C), James;
OL,8,FBrooks, Wilson, D James; Johnson.
OL,10,FBosnia-Herzegovina: Vasilj;
OL,11,FMuharemnovic, Katic, Kolasinac; Memic,
OL,12,FTahirovic, Bajraktarevic, Sunjic,
OL,13,FDedic; Demirovic, Dzeko (C).
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G18/18
